  "industry_note": "UNS S41000 / EN 1.4006 / X12Cr13 / JIS SUS410 / KS STS410 — martensitic stainless (Cr 11.5-13.5, C 0.08-0.15). 200°C T: σy 1000 / UTS 1350 / HRC 41. Tmax 600°C (over-tempering 위쪽). Cutlery, steam turbine blade, valve stem, oil/gas tubing."
